‚ä¢ context
  yield schema ‚â° cells(id, program_id, name, body_type, body, state), givens(id, cell_id, source_cell, source_field, is_optional), yields(id, cell_id, field_name, value_text, is_frozen), oracles(id, cell_id, oracle_type, assertion, condition_expr), cell_claims(cell_id, piston_id, claimed_at), ready_cells VIEW (cells with all non-optional givens frozen)
  yield runtime ‚â° Go + Dolt (MySQL wire protocol). Hard cells freeze inline. Soft cells dispatch to LLM pistons. Oracles checked on submit. Atomic claiming via INSERT IGNORE on cell_claims.

